        <Parent_String>fixed-wing aircraft by wing design [300233997], fixed-wing aircraft [300220417], heavier than air aircraft [300216063], aircraft by form [300220406], aircraft [300212527], air and space transportation vehicles [300222210], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
